abusinessl: Sourcenext Corp, headquartered in Tokyo, Japan, is engaged in the planning, development of personal computer (PC) software. Its software development methods include in-house development, outsourcing development and commercialization of products by acquiring licenses from other companies. The Company sells its products through stores and online shops. The products include security software Virus Security ZERO, postcard creation software HITSUOH series, portable document format (PDF) creation software IKINARI PDF series, game software TOKU-UCHI series, cellular phone-related software KEIKAI DENWA series, utility software KYOSOKU series and English learning software CHOUJIMAKU, among others. The Company was founded in 1996.
